INGREDIENTS LIST: Chicken Curry (57%), Cooked Basmati Rice (43%).

Chicken Curry contains: Water, Cooked RSPCA Approved Australian Chicken (17%), Diced Tomato (13%) [Tomato, Acidity Regulator (330), Mineral Salt (509)], Onion, Cream (Milk), Tomato Paste, Canola Oil, Garlic Paste, Ginger Paste, Corn Starch, Vegetable ;Stock Seasoning [contains Natural Flavouring], Sugar, Salt, Paprika, Cumin, Chilli Powder, Fennel, Coriander, Garam Masala, Turmeric.

Cooked Basmati Rice contains: Basmati Rice, Canola Oil, Salt.
